<LP>
   CARTER HAWLEY HALE STORES Inc. (Los Angeles) -- H. Michael
Hecht, chairman and chief executive officer of this
retailer's Broadway-Southern California division, was
additionally named an executive vice president at the parent.
Mr. Hecht, 50 years old, will continue to be principally
responsible for the Broadway-Southern California operations.
